The structure of `IntegralLattice.tensorAdelesEquivRestrictedProduct` is `E := P₁ ≪≫ₗ P₂`, where `P₁` is `TensorProduct.prodRight ℤ ℤ (IntegralLattice ℤ ℚ V) _ _` and `P₂` is `LinearEquiv.prodCongr (.refl _ _) <| RestrictedProduct.lTensorEquiv ℤ (IntegralLattice ℤ ℚ V) ...`.

